data.description: THREE BEDROOM FURNISHED END MODEL UNIT, INCLUDES PVT ELEVATOR! READY TO CLOSE ASAP. Brand new luxury townhomes each with private 2-car attached garage. Location! 1 block to Augusta Road, 3 blocks to Fluor Field, 3 blocks to Swamp Rabbit Trail, 1 block to County Square—soon under development as the new heart of GVL’s Downtown.10 ft ceilings on main floor, 9 ft & vaulted on the 2nd level, site-finished RECLAIMED hardwoods, ventless gas logs, and optional upgrades such as imported Turkish encaustic tile. Modern, open living space including eat-in granite kitchen w/stainless appliances FROM THE COOK'S STATION. Spacious master with luxurious private bath & private laundry & balcony. Main level patio perfect for entertaining. Luxury, convenience and YOUR OWN PRIVATE TWO CAR GARAGE.
